data.eml:eml: A new species of Mymar (Hymenoptera: Mymaridae) from the Palaearctic region, with nomenclatural changes in the genus

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Donev, Atanas D., Triapitsyn, Serguei V. (2010): A new species of Mymar (Hymenoptera: Mymaridae) from the Palaearctic region, with nomenclatural changes in the genus. Zootaxa 2644: 64-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.198645
